BlackRock Private Equity Partners

                    BlackRock Private Equity Partners (BlackRock PEP) manages the private capital fund of funds of BlackRock Alternative Advisors and specializes in managing diversified private equity portfolios that include primary, secondary and direct co-investments. The firm specializes in non-public investments. They participate in venture capital opportunities, growth capital financings, LBOs, mezzanine financings, distressed private equity transactions/funds and closed-end fund of funds investments. BlackRock PEP's investment process is based on fundamental due diligence and research that seeks to identify successful private equity funds and direct co-investment opportunities across a wide variety of industries, geographies and investment strategies.                  




