                    BlackRock CoRI Funds operates as a Open-End Investment Fund/Trust. The Trust currently offers shares of five series: BlackRock CoRI 2015 Fund, BlackRock CoRI 2017 Fund, BlackRock CoRI 2019 Fund, BlackRock CoRI 2021 Fund and BlackRock CoRI 2023 Fund. It was founded on July 26, 2013 and is headquartered in Wilmington, DE.                  




